Yes, this is in chronological order

* Sending colors

* Redesign the conversation window to use icons

* Filter for history, and better looking text in the history window

* Threaded group view option (with tooltips!)

* Acceleration keys

* Sending multi-recipient messages

* Sending and receiving contacts

* Fix up chat window and add in all the chat features

* Pretty up the file window (the one that shows the stats)

* SAR Manager, Auto-away

* Add in icon themes and maybe sound themes

* SOCKS5 Configuration and lots of other options

* Documentation

* Release it eventually
